Worked perfectly on (English) Win XP SP3. Word Magic is by far the best and most comprehensive translator for English -> Spanish and Spanish -> English. There are programs that do more languages, but this one catches all the subtleties of real speech, even has decent slang translations. Excellent resource for English speakers to learn Spanish, or Spanish speakers to learn English. Been running 4.0 for forever, so this is a welcome upgrade, even tho not the absolute latest version. Great download, Thanks!
